high_descs: Turn around and walk into the bedroom and turn left to reach the closet shelf.
Pick up the yellow apple from the shelf.
Turn around to exit the room and turn right to exit the bedroom and walk right to reach the pan.
Put the apple in the pan on the table.
Walk to the opposite side of the coffeetable.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Walk to the opposite of the table to face the pan.
Cut the apple into pieces with the knife.
Put the knife on the pan.
Pick up the pan from the table.
Turn left to walk up to the countertop with the microwave.
Put the pan on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Put the apple on the pan and cut it up with the knife on the countertop.

high_descs: Go to a room that is almost right behind you, walk straight down the hallway to the wall, enter a tiny room on the left, and approach the shelves.
Pick up an apple from the shelf.
Leave the room and then the hallway through the entrance you entered, go all the way to a lamp and then right to a table with a pan on it.
Place the apple on the pan.
Walk along the coffeetable to its opposite side.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Walk back to the apple.
Cut the apple with the knife.
Stick the knife in the pan.
Pick up the pan from the table.
Head right towards the countertop.
Place the pan on the countertop next to the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the apple on the pan on the countertop.

high_descs: Turn right toward the room beside the sofa, go to the lamp in the corner and turn left to the shelf.
Pick up the apple from the shelf.
Turn around, go to the lamp and turn right, go to the doorway and turn right, then go to the pan on the coffee table in front of the sofa.
Place the apple in the pan on the coffee table.
Go around to the front of the coffee table closer to the sofa.
Pick up the knife from the coffee table.
Go around the coffee table to the apple in the pan.
Slice the apple on the coffee table in the pan.
Place the knife in the pan with the apple.
Pick up the pan with the apple and knife in it.
Turn right and go across to the counter top
Place the pan on the counter top to the right of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with a knife and sliced apple in it on the counter top.
